{"word":"ἑωλοκρασία","slug":"ἑωλοκρασία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n46034\" key=\"e(wlokrasi/a\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἑωλο-κρᾱσία</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">κρᾶσις</etym>) <sense id=\"n46034.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">mixture of dregs, heel-taps</tr_>, etc., with which the drunken were dosed at the end of a revel by their strongerheaded companions: metaph., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἑωλοκρασίαν τινά μου τῆς πονηρίας κατασκεδάσας</foreign> having discharged <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the stale dregs</tr_> of his rascality over me, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:50\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.50</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Harp.</author></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg015:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Symp.\">Symp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3</biblScope> </bibl>; also, <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">κραιπάλη, ἐμμένει τὸ . . δυσάρεστον, ὥσπερ ἑ. τις ὕβρεως ἢ ὀργῆς</ref> </xr> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.148a</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}